reviewText: I was counting on a great performance, as usual, from Mr. Brown. Did not like his characterization in this one at all. Would not recommend.

Jokes & puns fly fast & furious from the amazing & innately-funny Joe E. Brown.  Bela Lugosi appears.  I found myself laughing at least once every two minutes.  Many of the jokes are extremely witty...but fly by fast.  Pay attention & laugh!
